com.versant.common.dataservice
Interface VDSIObjectManagerListener

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.EventListener
public interface VDSIObjectManagerListener
extends java.util.EventListener

This interface must be implemented by listeners interested in events raised by VDSObjectManager such as class creation, object creation, object deletion and object update

See Also:
VDSObjectManager, VDSObject,
